tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE video_performance_reports (
    report_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    video_id INT NOT NULL,
    date DATE NOT NULL,
    views INT NOT NULL,
    clicks INT NOT NULL,
    conversions INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE VideoPerformanceReports (
  report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  video_id INT,
  video_title VARCHAR(255),
  views_count INT,
  likes_count INT,
  dislikes_count INT,
  created_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE VideoCampaignMetrics (
  campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  video_id INT,
  impressions_count INT,
  clicks_count INT,
  conversion_rate FLOAT,
  marketing_cost DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE video_performance_reports (
    report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    video_id UUID NOT NULL,
    report_date DATE NOT NULL,
    views INT DEFAULT 0,
    clicks INT DEFAULT 0
);

CREATE TABLE video_metadata (
    video_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    duration INT,
    upload_date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE marketing_strategies (
    strategy_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    strategy_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    budget DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE VideoPerformanceReports (
  video_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  video_title VARCHAR(255),
  views_count INT,
  likes_count INT,
  dislikes_count INT,
  upload_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE MarketingStrategies (
  strategy_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  strategy_name VARCHAR(255),
  platform VARCHAR(50),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE VideoDetails (
  video_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  video_description TEXT,
  duration INT,
  category VARCHAR(100),
  tags VARCHAR[],
  views_count INT,
  likes_count INT,
  dislikes_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE ReportGenerationLogs (
  log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  report_type VARCHAR(50),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  user_id UUID,
  status VARCHAR(50)
);
